---
import MathPageLayout from '../../../layouts/MathPageLayout.astro';
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';
---

<MathPageLayout title="유형 04. 0/0 꼴 다항식 [하]">
  <CornellNote title="유형 04. 0/0 꼴 다항식 [하]" chapter="Level: Low">
<div slot="cues">
<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🟢 기본 원리</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>인수분해를 통한 공통인수 제거</li>
					<li>{ "$ x \to a $" } 대입 시 { "$ x-a $" } 찾기</li>
				</ul>
  </div>

  <section>
<div class="type-section">
					<p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">가장 기본적인 인수분해 연습입니다. 분모를 0으로 만드는 원인을 제거해 보세요.</p>
					
					<!-- Q1 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q1.</b> 극한값 { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 1} \\frac{x^2 - 1}{x - 1} $" }을 구하시오.</p>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type06-low/q1" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Q2 -->
			<div class="question-card">
				<div class="question-header">
					<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q2.</b> 극한값 { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 2} \\frac{x^2 + x - 6}{x - 2} $" }을 구하시오.</p>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type06-low/q2" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Q3 -->
			<div class="question-card">
				<div class="question-header">
					<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q3.</b> 극한값 { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to -1} \\frac{x^2 + 3x + 2}{x + 1} $" }을 구하시오.</p>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type06-low/q3" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
				</div>
			</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-top: 40px; display: flex; gap: 15px;">
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type04/" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none;">← 핵심 문제로 이동</a>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-const/" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none;">목록으로 돌아가기</a>
				</div>
  </section>
  </CornellNote>
</MathPageLayout>

<style>
.sol-button {
				display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; background: #eef7ee; color: #2e7d32;
				border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: bold;
				margin-left: 10px; border: 1.5px solid #2e7d32; transition: all 0.2s ease;
			}
			.sol-button:hover { background: #2e7d32; color: white; transform: translateY(-1px); }
</style>
